00:37:00,899 --> 00:37:03,039
In the world, you shall have tribulation.

751
00:37:03,039 --> 00:37:08,039
But in me, Jesus said, my peace give I unto you.

752
00:37:08,319 --> 00:37:10,159
We can have that peace.

753
00:37:10,159 --> 00:37:13,959
Listen, as the people of God saved, redeemed, reconciled,

754
00:37:13,959 --> 00:37:15,939
the Lord is my peace.

755
00:37:15,939 --> 00:37:19,039
The reality is that we ought to live in this world

756
00:37:19,039 --> 00:37:21,039
as we deal with whatever we deal with

757
00:37:21,039 --> 00:37:25,159
with allowing the peace of God to rule in our hearts.

758
00:37:26,019 --> 00:37:26,859
Why?

759
00:37:26,859 --> 00:37:29,239
Because my God's in control.

760
00:37:29,239 --> 00:37:31,519
And my God doeth all things well.

761
00:37:31,519 --> 00:37:33,359
He knows exactly where I am.

762
00:37:33,359 --> 00:37:35,239
He knows exactly what's going on.

763
00:37:35,239 --> 00:37:37,279
He knows exactly what I need.

764
00:37:37,279 --> 00:37:38,919
And he is able.

765
00:37:38,919 --> 00:37:40,439
He is able, amen.

766
00:37:40,439 --> 00:37:43,179
We sing the song, he is able to deliver thee.

767
00:37:43,179 --> 00:37:45,799
Every time we sing the song, I think about Daniel.

768
00:37:47,299 --> 00:37:49,479
And then I'm reminded that he's able to deliver me

769
00:37:49,479 --> 00:37:51,199
from what, from anything.

770
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:52,499
He's able.

771
00:37:52,499 --> 00:37:55,119
Sometimes he chooses to deliver us through something

772
00:37:55,119 --> 00:37:56,739
instead of from something.

773
00:37:57,839 --> 00:37:59,679
And in fact, I've learned in my life

774
00:37:59,679 --> 00:38:02,199
that when he delivers me through something,

775
00:38:02,199 --> 00:38:04,539
I learn a whole lot more about who my God is

776
00:38:04,539 --> 00:38:09,539
and how great he is when he delivers me through the storm.

777
00:38:10,619 --> 00:38:12,159
Jehovah shalom.

778
00:38:12,159 --> 00:38:14,119
The Lord is peace.

779
00:38:14,119 --> 00:38:15,839
Do you have peace with God tonight?

780
00:38:15,839 --> 00:38:17,599
You know for sure that heaven's your home.

781
00:38:17,599 --> 00:38:19,419
You have peace with God.

782
00:38:19,419 --> 00:38:23,919
If you do, are you allowing the peace of God

783
00:38:23,919 --> 00:38:25,439
to rule in your hearts?

784
00:38:26,439 --> 00:38:30,159
In me, you shall have peace.

785
00:38:30,159 --> 00:38:31,899
The world, you're gonna have tribulation.

786
00:38:31,899 --> 00:38:33,799
We see it, we understand it.

787
00:38:33,799 --> 00:38:35,159
But are we allowing the peace of God

788
00:38:35,159 --> 00:38:37,079
which passeth all understanding

789
00:38:37,079 --> 00:38:38,699
to truly rule in our hearts?

790
00:38:38,699 --> 00:38:39,539
Let's pray together.

791
00:38:39,539 --> 00:38:40,779
Father, we love you.

792
00:38:40,779 --> 00:38:41,879
We thank you for loving us.

793
00:38:41,879 --> 00:38:43,719
Thank you for your word.

794
00:38:43,719 --> 00:38:48,719
We thank you for the fact that you are our peace.

795
00:38:48,919 --> 00:38:50,559
God, if there's one that's not saved tonight,

796
00:38:50,559 --> 00:38:51,879
I pray that you'd help them to understand

797
00:38:51,879 --> 00:38:55,339
before they leave this place that they need to be saved.

798
00:38:56,179 --> 00:38:58,179
There's no other way to have peace with God

799
00:38:59,259 --> 00:39:01,859
except through the Lord Jesus Christ.

800
00:39:01,859 --> 00:39:03,699
It's through the blood of his cross

801
00:39:03,699 --> 00:39:07,859
that mankind, humanity, can have peace with thee.

802
00:39:07,859 --> 00:39:09,099
Lord, for those of us that know you

803
00:39:09,099 --> 00:39:10,419
as our personal Lord and Savior,

804
00:39:10,419 --> 00:39:14,419
we would say that we have that assurance of peace with you.

805
00:39:15,339 --> 00:39:16,859
Lord, help us to live each day

806
00:39:18,419 --> 00:39:21,339
with the peace of God ruling in our hearts.

807
00:39:21,339 --> 00:39:22,339
Bless our time of prayer.

808
00:39:22,339 --> 00:39:23,259
We thank you for it.

809
00:39:23,259 --> 00:39:24,579
We pray that you'd be honored and glorified

